data.description: That moment when the world stops and your jaw drops to the floor!  Yaaaaaasssss!  This is what you will experience when you walk into this STUNNING home!  Located in the highly COVETED Gated Piedmont and graciously sitting on a corner lot, this gorgeousness checks all the boxes.  The welcoming 2-STORY Grand Foyer will make your guests feel like royalty as they come in.  Behold, the staircase deserves a moment to pause as well!  An ample and spacious Formal Living & Dining Room for when you're feeling fancy or just want a more intimate place to converse or dine AND of course a super OPEN Family Room/Gourment Kitchen/Sunroom Combination for your day to day living without compromising on style or space.  This level also includes a very large laundry room/mud room with lots of space to unload your bags and lots of built in shelves in the laundry to keep everything organized and easy access to your front load garage.  The bedroom level is fully equipped with 4 bedrooms, including a mega SPACIOUS Primary Suite featuring a large WALK-IN closet with professional components to maximize its storage capacity and a well appointed bathroom with a large SOAK-IN TUB, double vanity, water closet, and great sized shower!  The shared bathroom is large and features double vanity and shower/tub combination to make bath time for the little ones a breeze! As you prepare to head downstairs, take a moment to admire the staircase again, take a deep breath, shoulders back, chest up, belly in, and now you may proceed to descend graciously and fabulously like the royalty you are!  The basement in this abode is completely open and has a lot of untapped potential!  There is rough-in for plumbing for an additional full bathroom so you can unleash your best HGTV inspiration and finish it to your own taste.  There's also plenty of unfinished space to carve in an additional room in case you need more space.  The french doors let in a lot of natural light and make it an easy transition into the backyard.  The outdoor space in this house absolutely does not disappoint, offering a beautifully manicured yard, a gorgeous low maintenance deck and a great patio.  Did I miss anything?!  Duh!  The community!!!  Your life is about to change for the better!  This highly sought after GATED neighborhood feautures an 18-Hole GOLF COURSE (separate membership available), Club House, Restaurant, Bar, Fitness Center with a great scheduled of work out sessions, 3 SWIMMING POOLS, including an indoor one, Tennis Court, Basketball Court and multiple ponds to soften the landscape.  The community also boasts miles and miles of walking trails, multiple playground areas for the little ones and lots of activities planned throughout the year to keep the residents involved and engaged.  The moment is here, and you have arrived!  Welcome Home!
